# Peridot
Test K8 Environment for Peridot 

HA Kubeadm Cluster to be Built in our Test Environment:

Naming All Nodes after the elements that Peridot is made of

Kubernetes v1.26.1
1x HAproxy and Ansible Node (4 GB RAM / 2 CPU) - Tectonic
3x Worker Nodes (16 GB RAM / 4 CPU) - Iron, Magnesium, Silicon
3x Control Plane Nodes with (6 GB RAM / 2 CPU) - Hydrogen, Oxygen, Chromite

